Package: signalbeam-agent
Version: 0.1.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH_PLACEHOLDER
Maintainer: SignalBeam <support@signalbeam.io>
Depends: docker.io | docker-ce
Recommends: curl
Description: SignalBeam Edge Agent - Manage edge devices from the cloud
 The SignalBeam Edge Agent is a lightweight daemon that runs on edge devices
 (e.g., Raspberry Pi, mini-PCs) and communicates with the SignalBeam cloud
 platform for fleet management, monitoring, and containerized application
 deployment.
 .
 Features:
  - Device registration and authentication
  - Automatic heartbeat and health monitoring
  - Container reconciliation and management
  - Metrics collection (CPU, memory, disk)
  - Automatic updates and rollouts
Homepage: https://signalbeam.io
